	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod tanto tempore literis tuis ad me novissimis nihil responderim, caussam ex <persName type="auto_name">Simlero</persName> tuo vel etiam meo nunc cognosces.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Igitur, tametsi te pridem rescivisse puto, quae ex me scire cupiebas, ac longe fortasse etiam certiora, quam ego tibi scribere queam, scribam tamen, quę hactenus scire potui, idque Germanice; nam hoc te velle ex literis tuis cognovi."</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es ist mir von meins g[nädigen] hern hof geschriben worden, wie ain junger vom adel, mit nammen Bat <persName type="citizen_name">Wilhelm von Bonstetten</persName> von <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName>, so ain zeyt lang an gemelten meins g[nädigen] h[ern] hof gewesen, alda von menigklichem lieb und werd gehalten, des vorndrigen jars mit grafe <persName type="citizen_name">Bastian von Helffenstein</persName> in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l869" cert="high">Sybenbirgen</placeName> zogen sey, und wie er dadennen widerum mit andern frisch und gesund ins land <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l609" cert="high">Wirttemberg</placeName> khummen, hab er sich nit weyter an den hof wellen begeben, sonder sey mit etlichen margraf <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18422">Albrechten von Brandenburg</persName> zuͦgezogen; da sage man, er sey umbkhummen."</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec, quoniam incerta sunt, non destiti porro investigare; itaque accepi, quosdam in oppido ducatus huius esse, cui nomen <placeName ref="l1913" cert="high">Schorndorf</placeName>, qui <persName type="citizen_name">Beato</persName> comites in militiam posteriorem fuerint.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad quos scripsi me ea de re bona fide certiorem scripto meis impensis facerent.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Id simulatque accepero (expe[c]to autem in dies), ad te primo quoque et nuncio et tempore mittam.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim vale, vir doctissime atque optime, sitque officium <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8113" cert="high">Volmarii</persName> tibi cordi semper.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l512" cert="high">Tubinge</placeName> sexto decimo calendas februarii anno etc 59.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tui nominis studiosissimus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8113" cert="high">Melchior Volmarius Rufus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Eximia doctrina, pietate et dignitate viro d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, ecclesiae <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinae</placeName> pastori fidelissimo, d. et amico honorando suo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
